"能力说明\n• 世界书会根据触发规则在发送消息时自动注入上下文。\n• 它是“静态规则知识”，不参与记忆系统写入。\n\n怎么用（建议顺序）\n1. 先导入世界书（支持 JSON/PNG 或 URL）。\n2. 在“当前会话”绑定需要生效的世界书。\n3. 按需启用“隔离发送”，让会话只发送提示词与世界书上下文。\n\n关键参数与状态\n• 绑定数量：显示当前会话已绑定 / 总世界书数。\n• 启用条目：显示每本世界书里启用条目占比。\n• 已启用隔离发送：会屏蔽记忆、MCP、快捷指令等外部工具上下文。\n\n管理建议\n• 大型世界书优先维护条目启用状态，避免注入冗余内容。\n• 导入后先看“最近导入结果”，及时处理失败条目和冲突。\n• 重要世界书建议定期导出备份。" = "What it does\n• Worldbooks inject context automatically when messages are sent based on trigger rules.\n• They are static rule knowledge and do not write to the memory system.\n\nHow to use (recommended order)\n1. Import a worldbook first (JSON/PNG or URL supported).\n2. Bind the worldbooks that should apply to the current session.\n3. Enable isolated sending when needed so the session sends only prompts and worldbook context.\n\nKey parameters and status\n• Binding count: current session bindings / total worldbooks.\n• Enabled entries: enabled entry ratio for each worldbook.\n• Isolated sending enabled: blocks memory, MCP, Shortcuts, and other external tool context.\n\nManagement tips\n• For large worldbooks, maintain entry enabled states first to avoid redundant injections.\n• After importing, check Recent Import Result to handle failed entries and conflicts.\n• Export important worldbooks regularly as backups.";
"能力说明\n• 记忆系统会在每次回复前参与检索，帮助模型关联你过去的偏好与上下文。\n• 与“世界书”不同，记忆系统是可持续积累、可读可写的动态知识。\n\n关键开关\n• 启用记忆功能：总开关。关闭后不会检索、也不会写入新记忆。\n• 允许写入新的记忆：仅控制“写入”，关闭后仍可读取已有记忆。\n\n推荐用法\n1. 先开启总开关观察回答是否更贴合长期习惯。\n2. 如果担心噪声记忆，先关闭写入，仅保留读取。\n3. 通过“记忆库管理”定期清理低质量或过时记忆。\n\n常见问题\n• 回答变得重复：可能记忆冗余，建议进入记忆库整理。\n• 明明开了但没效果：先确认会话未被世界书隔离策略屏蔽相关工具。" = "What it does\n• The memory system participates in retrieval before each reply, helping the model connect your past preferences and context.\n• Unlike worldbooks, memory is dynamic knowledge that can be accumulated, read, and written.\n\nKey switches\n• Enable memory: the master switch. When off, memory is not retrieved or written.\n• Allow writing new memories: controls writing only; existing memories can still be read when off.\n\nRecommended use\n1. Turn on the master switch first and see whether replies better match long-term habits.\n2. If noisy memories are a concern, disable writing and keep reading only.\n3. Use Memory Library Management regularly to clean low-quality or outdated memories.\n\nCommon issues\n• Repetitive answers may indicate redundant memories; organize them in the memory library.\n• If it is enabled but has no effect, check whether session isolation from worldbooks is blocking related tools.";
"让 AI 在多轮对话里持续记住你的偏好、背景与目标。" = "Let AI keep remembering your preferences, background, and goals across conversations.";
"语音朗读（TTS）" = "Speech playback (TTS)";
"这个页面适合做什么\n• 集中管理非核心聊天流程的进阶能力。\n• 快速进入维护、导入、调试等工具入口。\n\n各入口怎么选\n• 反馈助手：提交问题和追踪处理进度。\n• 远程文件访问：在局域网内访问 Documents 做排查或批量处理。\n• 存储管理：清理模型、文件、缓存，回收空间。\n• 导入数据：导入 ETOS 导出包或第三方应用迁移数据。\n\n使用建议\n• 不常用的功能可按需开启，避免主流程过载。\n• 涉及导入与清理时，建议先备份关键数据再执行。" = "What this page is for\n• Manage advanced capabilities outside the core chat flow.\n• Quickly open maintenance, import, debugging, and other tool entries.\n\nChoosing entries\n• Feedback Assistant: submit issues and track progress.\n• Remote File Access: access Documents on the local network for diagnosis or batch work.\n• Storage Management: clean models, files, and caches to recover space.\n• Import Data: import ETOS packages or migrate from third-party apps.\n\nTips\n• Enable less-used features only when needed to keep the main flow focused.\n• Back up important data before import or cleanup operations.";
"这里集中放置进阶能力、调试入口与跨平台工具集成。" = "Advanced capabilities, debugging entries, and cross-platform tool integrations are collected here.";
"适用场景\n• 你希望让模型调用 iOS 快捷指令完成自动化任务。\n• 你需要统一管理导入来源、启用状态和运行模式。\n\n怎么用（建议顺序）\n1. 先在“官方导入快捷指令”下载并运行导入助手。\n2. 再用“从剪贴板导入清单”批量导入工具定义。\n3. 打开“向模型暴露快捷指令工具”总开关。\n4. 逐个工具检查描述、启用状态和运行模式。\n\n导入模式说明\n• 轻度导入：只导入名称，适合先快速接入。\n• 深度导入：尝试解析 iCloud 分享内容并生成描述；失败会自动降级为仅链接。\n\n关键参数说明\n• 导入快捷指令名称：用于匹配官方导入助手名称。\n• 桥接快捷指令名称：桥接执行链路所用的快捷指令名称。\n• 运行模式（单工具）：\n  - 直连优先：先尝试直接执行，再回退桥接。\n  - 桥接优先：先走桥接，再回退直连。\n• 倒计时自动批准：审批等待秒数，范围 1~30 秒。\n\n常见问题\n• 工具没被调用：先查总开关是否开启、单项是否启用。\n• 导入失败：看“最近导入结果”中的新增/跳过/无效和冲突名称。\n• 执行超时：优先确认快捷指令本身可独立运行，再检查桥接名称是否一致。\n• urlshim / URL Scheme 跳转失败：回到本页先复制清单到剪贴板，再点“从剪贴板导入清单”即可继续。" = "When to use this\n• You want the model to call iOS Shortcuts for automation tasks.\n• You need to manage import sources, enabled states, and run modes in one place.\n\nHow to use (recommended order)\n1. Download and run the import helper from Official Import Shortcut.\n2. Use Import List from Clipboard to bulk import tool definitions.\n3. Turn on the master switch that exposes Shortcut tools to the model.\n4. Review each tool description, enabled state, and run mode.\n\nImport modes\n• Light import: imports names only, good for quick setup.\n• Deep import: tries to parse iCloud shares and generate descriptions; falls back to link-only on failure.\n\nKey parameters\n• Import shortcut name: used to match the official import helper.\n• Bridge shortcut name: the shortcut used by the bridge execution path.\n• Run mode (per tool):\n  - Direct first: try direct execution first, then fall back to bridge.\n  - Bridge first: use bridge first, then fall back to direct.\n• Countdown auto-approval: approval wait time from 1 to 30 seconds.\n\nCommon issues\n• Tool not called: check the master switch and the individual enabled state.\n• Import failed: review Added / Skipped / Invalid and conflict names in Recent Import Result.\n• Execution timeout: confirm the shortcut itself can run, then check bridge name consistency.\n• If urlshim / URL Scheme fails to open on iPhone, copy the list to the clipboard on this page and use Import List from Clipboard.";
"适用场景\n• 你想快速判断“当前会话到底能用哪些工具”。\n• 你想统一调整不同类型工具的启用与审批策略。\n\n页面怎么看\n• 配置已启用：表示你在设置层面已打开。\n• 当前会话可用：在“总开关 + 审批策略 + 会话隔离”等条件下，聊天时真的可用。\n• 两个数字不一致通常不是 bug，而是被会话条件限制（例如世界书隔离发送）。\n\n推荐使用流程\n1. 先看概览区，确认五类工具的可用数量。\n2. 用“仅显示已启用”快速聚焦当前生效配置。\n3. 分别进入内置/拓展/MCP/Skills/快捷指令分类做单项微调。\n\n关键开关说明\n• 启用记忆系统：决定记忆相关内置工具是否可参与聊天。\n• 各分类“向模型暴露…工具”：控制该类工具是否整体开放给模型。\n• 审批策略：决定调用前是否确认、自动通过或拒绝。\n\n排查建议\n• 工具不生效：优先核对“当前会话可用”而不是“配置已启用”。\n• 会话隔离提示为橙色时：记忆、MCP、Agent Skills、快捷指令会被会话级策略屏蔽。" = "When to use this\n• You want to quickly see which tools the current session can actually use.\n• You want to adjust enabled states and approval policies for different tool types in one place.\n\nHow to read the page\n• Configured enabled: enabled at the settings level.\n• Available in current session: actually usable after master switches, approval policies, and session isolation.\n• Different numbers are usually not a bug; session conditions such as isolated worldbook sending may limit availability.\n\nRecommended flow\n1. Check the overview first to confirm available counts for the five tool groups.\n2. Use Show Enabled Only to focus on active configuration.\n3. Enter Built-in / Extension / MCP / Skills / Shortcuts categories for item-level tuning.\n\nKey switches\n• Enable memory: controls whether memory-related built-in tools can participate in chat.\n• Expose tools to model switches: control whether each category is open to the model.\n• Approval policy: controls whether calls require confirmation, auto-allow, or deny.\n\nTroubleshooting\n• If a tool does not work, check Available in current session before Configured enabled.\n• When the isolation notice is orange, memory, MCP, Agent Skills, and Shortcuts may be blocked by session policy.";
"适用场景\n• 你想把外部服务能力接入聊天（例如检索、执行工具、读取资源）。\n• 你需要快速定位“为什么工具没被模型调用”这类问题。\n\n怎么用（建议顺序）\n1. 在“已配置服务器”添加或编辑 MCP Server，先确保连接正常。\n2. 打开“向模型暴露 MCP 工具”，否则聊天阶段不会调用 MCP。\n3. 在“连接概览”确认“已连接数量 / 参与聊天数量”。\n4. 用“快速调试”先做一次手动调用，确认参数、返回和超时策略都正常。\n\n关键参数说明\n• 倒计时自动批准：自动审批等待秒数，范围 1~30 秒。\n• 工具 ID：必须填写服务端公布的 toolId。\n• 工具 Payload（JSON）：调用参数对象，必须是合法 JSON 字典。\n• 资源 ID：资源读取标识符。\n• 资源 Query（JSON）：可选查询参数，留空等价于不传。\n\n常见状态解读\n• 已连接并参与聊天：可被模型正常调用。\n• 已连接：可调试，但当前未参与聊天。\n• 重连中 / 失败：优先检查 Endpoint、鉴权头和网络可达性。\n\n排查建议\n• 模型不调用工具：先看总开关、工具是否启用、审批策略是否 alwaysDeny。\n• 调用失败：看“活跃调用”“治理日志”“最新响应”三处信息定位。" = "When to use this\n• You want to connect external service capabilities to chat, such as retrieval, tool execution, or resource reading.\n• You need to quickly diagnose why tools are not being called by the model.\n\nHow to use (recommended order)\n1. Add or edit MCP Servers under Configured Servers and make sure they connect successfully.\n2. Turn on Expose MCP tools to model; otherwise MCP is not called during chat.\n3. Check Connected count / Chat participants in the connection overview.\n4. Use Quick Debug to make one manual call and verify parameters, results, and timeout policy.\n\nKey parameters\n• Countdown auto-approval: automatic approval wait time from 1 to 30 seconds.\n• Tool ID: must match the server-published toolId.\n• Tool Payload (JSON): call parameter object and must be a valid JSON dictionary.\n• Resource ID: resource read identifier.\n• Resource Query (JSON): optional query parameters; empty means no query.\n\nCommon status\n• Connected and participating in chat: can be called by the model.\n• Connected: can be debugged but is not participating in current chat.\n• Reconnecting / Failed: check endpoint, auth headers, and network reachability first.\n\nTroubleshooting\n• If the model does not call a tool, check the master switch, tool enabled state, and whether approval policy is alwaysDeny.\n• If a call fails, inspect Active calls, Governance log, and Latest response.";
"适用场景\n• 你想让模型在聊天时执行特定任务，例如格式化输出、代码检查、知识问答等。\n• 你希望将常用的提示词或操作封装为可复用的技能模块。\n\n怎么用（建议顺序）\n1. 点击\"新增技能\"粘贴 SKILL.md，或通过 GitHub / 本地文件导入。\n2. 确认技能列表中对应技能已启用（右侧开关为开）。\n3. 打开\"向模型暴露 Agent Skills（use_skill）\"总开关。\n4. 在聊天中告知模型你的需求，模型会在合适时机调用 use_skill。\n\nSKILL.md 格式说明\n• 文件头（frontmatter）必须包含 name 和 description 字段。\n• name 作为技能的唯一标识，不能与已有技能重名。\n• 正文可包含使用说明、参数说明、示例等任意 Markdown 内容。\n\n常见问题\n• 模型不调用技能：先检查总开关是否已开启，并确认对应技能已启用。\n• 导入失败：检查仓库地址是否可访问，或改用本地文件/手动粘贴 SKILL.md 内容。\n• 技能内容需更新：进入技能详情编辑 SKILL.md 文件即可。" = "When to use this\n• You want the model to perform specific tasks in chat, such as formatting output, code review, or knowledge Q&A.\n• You want to package common prompts or operations into reusable skill modules.\n\nHow to use (recommended order)\n1. Tap Add Skill to paste SKILL.md, or import from GitHub / local files.\n2. Confirm the skill is enabled in the skill list.\n3. Turn on the master switch that exposes Agent Skills (use_skill) to the model.\n4. Tell the model what you need in chat; it will call use_skill when appropriate.\n\nSKILL.md format\n• The frontmatter must include name and description.\n• name is the unique skill identifier and cannot duplicate an existing skill.\n• The body may contain usage instructions, parameter notes, examples, or any Markdown content.\n\nCommon issues\n• Model does not call a skill: check that the master switch and the individual skill are enabled.\n• Import failed: check repository access, or use local file / manual SKILL.md paste.\n• Need updates: edit SKILL.md from the skill detail page.";
"集中管理内置记忆、拓展工具、MCP、Agent Skills 与快捷指令的聊天暴露状态。" = "Manage chat exposure for built-in memory, extension tools, MCP, Agent Skills, and Shortcuts in one place.";

